<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV69">
<l>kārēṟ ṟiruṭceki lēṟṟiṉ cuṭaruk kuḷaintuvelvāṉ</l>
<l>pōrēṟ ṟetirntatu puṉṟalai mālai puvaṉiyellā</l>
<l>nīrēṟ ṟaḷanta neṭiya pirāṉaru ḷāviṭumē</l>
<l>vārēṟ ṟiḷamulai yāyvarun tēluṉ vaḷaittiṟamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The darkness of the cloud bull, suffering the glow of the red bull, faces [it],</l>
<l>taking up a fight in order to win. You with young breasts held up by straps,</l>
<l>if you suffer because of your bangles, as a grace the tall lord who, accepting</l>
<l>water, measured the whole earth, will let ruddy-headed evening pass.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
